title: [Tiffaine's Outfitting]
[Tiffaine's General Store]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  An aqua-hued seaglass display and a plain wooden table sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.
